{
  "stem": "214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That there's going to be a deportation from Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then maybe-- so we know, it really started a big again, panic.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody said, what shall we do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They probably won't take us, because we are working, blah, blah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And before you knew, there came, maybe two trucks, with German gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was the people from this book.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I probably would have just stood there and waited for them to take me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm-- I'm almost sure.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my friend, [NON-ENGLISH], she grabbed me by my arm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we started running-- the two of us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And not far from there, there was a farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she was really so intelligent-- [LAUGHS] --enterprising.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we ran into the barn of this farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went up quickly to the attic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We buried ourselves in the hay and were lying there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we heard shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard screams.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we heard-- and there we were lying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then it got dark, and it quieted down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there we were, still safe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had no idea what to do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, it must have been late-- it was dark already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It must have been pretty late.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We hear somebody comes to the barn and says-- see, this was another-- we never-- we never took his name.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I have no idea who it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he says, if anybody is here, I am leaving some milk and bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I will come back tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if this bread and milk are gone, I assume that someone is there, and I will be coming back every evening with milk and bread.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were lying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the deportation was taking place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
